Data for Northwest Territories includes Nunavut, from 1993-01 to 1998-12.

This real-time table is designed to track changes in the estimates since their initial release. Typically, data are released as preliminary for a specific period, revised the following period based on new information and eventually revised in an annual or historical revision process. Additional information can be found in the Real-time tables (opens new window). article."
Data for this Canadian industry are presented in unadjusted form as there is no seasonal pattern established by official statistics yet.

Data for oilseed and grain merchant wholesalers were included from January 2023, while those for petroleum, petroleum products, and other hydrocarbons merchant wholesalers were included from March 2023.
